section.para:
For each ,
Gradle will create a task named assembleDependents${component.name}${binary.variant}
that assembles (compile and link) the binary and all of its dependent binaries.

For each ,
Gradle will create a task named assembleDependents${component.name}
that assembles all the binaries of the component and all of their dependent binaries.

For each ,
Gradle will create a task named buildDependents${component.name}${binary.variant}
that builds (compile, link and check) the binary and all of its dependent binaries.

For each ,
Gradle will create a task named buildDependents${component.name}
that builds all the binaries of the component and all of their dependent binaries.
